2025-11-05ESDCDepartment of Employment and Social Development ActReappointment of a part-time member of the Social Security Tribunal who may hear matters in the Employment Insurance SectionReappointment of Paul William Dusome of Barrie, Ontario, as a part-time member of the Social Security Tribunal who may hear matters in the Employment Insurance Section, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of two years, effective December 15, 2025.N/A
act: Department of Employment and Social Development Act
subject: Reappointment of a part-time member of the Social Security Tribunal who may hear matters in the Employment Insurance Section
precis: Reappointment of Paul William Dusome of Barrie, Ontario, as a part-time member of the Social Security Tribunal who may hear matters in the Employment Insurance Section, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of two years, effective December 15, 2025.
